      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（無事に海外ツアーが終わって、LizNoirは）\n（MV撮影に向けて練習をしているようだが……）",
      "startTime": 4.8094138234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……ふぅ……",
      "startTime": 8.1162132581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（相当激しく追い込んでいるんだな。こころだけ）\n（じゃない、LizNoir全員が疲弊している……）",
      "startTime": 17,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……今回のMVのダンス……\n結構、大変かも、ですね……",
      "startTime": 25.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "でもっ！　こんなところでへこたれませんよ～！\nさぁ、もう一回今の動き合わせましょう！",
      "startTime": 34.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（めずらしいな、普段のこころだったら「もう疲れた～）\n（莉央さんの鬼ー！」とか言って音を上げるのに）",
      "startTime": 43.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、今のワンフレーズ、もうちょっと粘りませんか？\nもっともっと素敵な動きになると思うんです！",
      "startTime": 51.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、こころ達はBIG4なんですから～\n愛ちゃんも動いた動いたっ！",
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "さぁさぁ～\n次期センターのこころに続いて下さい～",
      "startTime": 62.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（杞憂だったみたいで良かった）\n（本当に……成長したな）",
      "startTime": 69.5304707422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
